fsce_tidy

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 250 rows and 18 columns.

Source

Generated by data-raw/fsce_tidy.R.

Details

Variables include:

  • cell_id

  • UMAP dimensions (UMAP1 and UMAP2)

  • k-means clusters (k_cluster)

  • Top ten most variable activities (Uracil_45, riboG_44, etc.)
